chapters.title: Darrell Goes Back to School with Felicity

tracks.title: Darrell Goes Back to School with Felicity

metadata.description: Welcome to Malory Towers, where there's more to life than lessons! Darrell Rivers is delighted to be Head Girl of her form - and this year her sister Felicity joins Malory Towers, too. Most of the time Darrell couldn't be prouder of Felicity, but she's much less keen on her sister's trouble-making new friend. With twins Connie and Ruth also causing problems, Darrell's first term in charge is a big challenge....
metadata.author: Enid Blyton
